  "titles": "Ezekyle Abaddon First Captain of the Sons of Horus, High Marshal of the Justaerin",
  "lore": "Ezekyle Abaddon was one of the foremost warriors of the Sons of Horus and commander of the elite Justaerin Terminators. He echoed his Primarch in many ways, not least in his savage power as a fighter and skill as a tactician, which gave him the greatest tally of victories of any within the Sons of Horus bar his Primarch. Once regarded as a hero of the Imperium, Abaddon was devoted to Horus always and walked willingly into damnation with his master, his name becoming among the most feared and despised of those that turned Traitor and was personally responsible for destroying many of his former comrades who remained loyal.",
